🤖 Alibaba Qwen Launches Qwen3-Plus

@Alibaba_Qwen introduced Qwen3-Plus, a multimodal agent model that combines vision, language and coding capabilities.

The model supports GUI and CLI tasks, visual reasoning, search-augmented QA and agent workflows, and is now available via API on Alibaba Cloud Model Studio.

