1/5 NVIDIA just released Polar — an RL training framework that doesn't require you to modify your agent harness at all.

It intercepts at the model API boundary instead. The harness runs exactly as it does in production.

Full technical breakdown with benchmark tables: https://t.co/qrOpiRxzgE

